<body>
  <h1>Module 6: Email Marketing</h1>

  <h2>What is Email Marketing?</h2>
  <p>Email marketing involves sending marketing or promotional messages to a group of people using email.</p>

  <h2>Building an Email List</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Website sign-up forms</li>
    <li>Social media contests and giveaways</li>
    <li>Pop-up offers</li>
    <li>Email marketing platforms</li>
    <li>Third-party providers</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Creating Effective Email Campaigns</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>**Subject Lines:** Write compelling subject lines that grab attention.</li>
    <li>**Engaging Content:** Create high-quality content that provides value.</li>
    <li>**Strong Call to Action:** Encourage readers to take action, such as making a purchase or signing up for a newsletter.</li>
    <li>**Mobile Optimization:** Ensure your emails are optimized for mobile devices.</li>
    <li>**Personalization:** Tailor your emails to individual preferences and behaviors.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Email Marketing Best Practices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>**Segmentation:** Divide your email list into segments based on demographics, interests, or behavior.</li>
    <li>**A/B Testing:** Experiment with different subject lines, content, and send times to optimize performance.</li>
    <li>**Timing:** Send emails at the optimal time to maximize engagement.</li>
    <li>**Frequency:** Determine the right frequency of emails to avoid overwhelming your subscribers.</li>
    <li>**Analytics:** Track key metrics like open rates, click-through rates, and conversion rates.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Email Marketing Automation</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>**Workflows:** Create automated workflows to trigger emails based on specific actions or events.</li>
    <li>**Welcome Emails:** Welcome new subscribers and provide value.</li>
    <li>**Abandoned Cart Emails:** Recover lost sales by reminding customers of items left in their cart.</li>
    <li>**Birthday Emails:** Send personalized birthday wishes and offers.</li>
    <li>**Anniversary Emails:** Celebrate customer anniversaries with special promotions.</li>
  </ul>
</body>
